## CLI cheat sheet

```bash
# Standalone invocations (CLI auto-generates a per-stage session log):
python -m harness verify-static  --service <svc>
python -m harness apply          --service <svc>
python -m harness verify-runtime --service <svc> --phase <phase> --sub-goal <svc>

# Orchestrator flow — share one session log across all three stages:
LOG=$(python -m harness session-path --service <svc>)
python -m harness verify-static  --service <svc> --session-log "$LOG"
python -m harness apply          --service <svc> --session-log "$LOG"
python -m harness verify-runtime --service <svc> --phase <p> --sub-goal <s> \
    --session-log "$LOG"
```

JSON envelope: `{service, stage, summary, passed, session_log, checks[]}`.
Exit codes: `0` pass · `1` at least one fail · `2` config error.
